### 建立帳號 (POST)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "username": "johndoe",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "teacher"
}

### 查詢全部帳號 (GET)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/accounts

### 查詢特定帳號 (GET)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/accounts/2

### 更新帳號 (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/accounts/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Updated",
  "username": "johnupdated",
  "password": "newpassword",
  "role": "student"
}

### 刪除帳號 (DELETE)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/accounts/1
